              pioneering 5-star pump manufacturer, contributing significantly to
              the nation's energy goals. His relentless pursuit of innovation
              earned nine patents, while advocating for equality shaped the
              company's values of respect, ethics, and customer-centricity.
            </p>
            <p>
              A committed family man, Mr. Patidar resides in Indore, cherishing
              moments with his family, reading, and traveling. Alongside
              chairing Shakti Pumps, he serves as the Chairman of FICCI, MP
